label("8",(0,4),W);
label("2",(2,3),S);
label("6",(4,3),E);
label("1",(.5,8),N);
label("1",(3.5,6),N);

[/asy] ||| To find the total length of the segments in Figure 2, we first note that the lengths are 8 (left side) + 6 (right side) + 1 (top right) and then add 1 from the top left side of Figure 1, totaling 16. So the answer is \boxed{16}.

